* ''[[Sports Illustrated]]'' [[Sportsman of the Year]]: 2008<ref>{{cite news |title=Michael Phelps Named Sports Illustrated Sportsman of the Year |url=http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/lane9/news/19721.asp |work=Swimming World |date=December 2, 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825214512/http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/lane9/news/19721.asp |archive-date=August 25, 2012 |access-date=September 5, 2010 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>
